    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，工党支持率下滑但仍遥遥领先保守党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-labour-slips-but-stays-way-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党的支持率跌至英国大选活动中的最差水平，彭博民意调查显示，其对里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的执政党保守党的领先优势也创下同期新低 — — 但尽管如此，工党领导人基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 仍然有望在周四的选举中赢得唐宁街 10 号的入主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-labour-slips-but-stays-way-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 10:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在英国大选最后冲刺中加剧恐惧因素</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/sunak-ramps-up-the-fear-factor-in-frantic-final-uk-election-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 加大力度煽动人们对工党占据绝对多数的担忧，试图在周四英国大选之前做最后的努力来提高保守党选民的投票率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/sunak-ramps-up-the-fear-factor-in-frantic-final-uk-election-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 10:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登辩论受阻 加文·纽森在中国获赞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/gavin-newsom-hailed-within-china-after-biden-s-debate-troubles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统乔·拜登的辩论表现糟糕之后，加文·纽森成为少数几个被提名接替他的人选之一。在中国，这将是一个受欢迎的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/gavin-newsom-hailed-within-china-after-biden-s-debate-troubles</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国劳动力市场出现失去动力的迹象，令美联储提高警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/fed-on-alert-for-us-labor-market-as-hiring-and-quitting-slow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着有迹象表明劳动力市场正在失去动力，经济学家和一些美联储官员越来越警惕，美国工人可能即将面临痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/fed-on-alert-for-us-labor-market-as-hiring-and-quitting-slow</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
