    <item>
      <title>法国各政党在选举最后阶段采取行动阻止勒庞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/main-french-parties-court-rivals-as-vote-heads-to-second-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的中间派联盟和左翼新人民阵线必须在今晚之前战略性地退出法国周日最后一轮选举的候选人，以做最后的努力阻止占主导地位的极右翼政党掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/main-french-parties-court-rivals-as-vote-heads-to-second-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 20:57:09 GMT</pubDate>
